#: model:ir.model.fields,help:report_xlsx.field_ir_actions_report__report_type
msgid ""
"The type of the report that will be rendered, each one having its own "
"rendering method. HTML means the report will be opened directly in your "
"browser PDF means the report will be rendered using Wkhtmltopdf and "
"downloaded by the user."
msgstr ""
"O tipo de informe que se representará, cada un co seu propio método de "
"representación. HTML significa que o informe se abrirá directamente no PDF "
"do seu navegador significa que o informe se representará usando Wkhtmltopdf "
"e o usuario descargarao."

